{"tid":524035,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"國際酒店萬豪集團被爆將港澳台及西藏列為「國家」","createTime":"2018-01-09T07:24:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-09T09:30:29.000Z","uid":32938,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"9184a73bc32720596ff8f90e487055f49b6e8f0b","tid":524035,"uid":32938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T07:24:50.000Z","msg":"據「環球時報」官方微博消息，網友@仲舉掃地 舉報稱，國際連鎖酒店萬豪@萬豪酒店及度假酒店 在中文版頁面中，公然將台灣、香港和澳門列為「國家」，甚至連西藏都出現在「國家」的選項中。<br />\n<br />\n萬豪集團旗下酒店包括JW萬豪酒店、麗思卡爾頓酒店、萬麗酒店、萬豪酒店、萬怡酒店、喜來登酒店、威斯汀酒店和W酒店等30個品牌，據官網顯示，目前該集團在華共有124家酒店。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://assets.wenweipo.com/image/2018/01/09/karljing_901e4d9972a4f552534929c8dfb30012.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fassets.wenweipo.com%2Fimage%2F2018%2F01%2F09%2Fkarljing_901e4d9972a4f552534929c8dfb30012.jpg&h=67ca7425&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://assets.wenweipo.com/image/2018/01/09/karljing_5923152406175182260cf69c056169f1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fassets.wenweipo.com%2Fimage%2F2018%2F01%2F09%2Fkarljing_5923152406175182260cf69c056169f1.jpg&h=ac101a58&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://assets.wenweipo.com/image/2018/01/09/karljing_53c2bbe6d1006fe0e687d193bc915aa3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fassets.wenweipo.com%2Fimage%2F2018%2F01%2F09%2Fkarljing_53c2bbe6d1006fe0e687d193bc915aa3.jpg&h=3c768b59&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://assets.wenweipo.com/image/2018/01/09/karljing_781c54bdb599f9f957bfee49b2a3cb0a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fassets.wenweipo.com%2Fimage%2F2018%2F01%2F09%2Fkarljing_781c54bdb599f9f957bfee49b2a3cb0a.jpg&h=f72b098a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0e69071e8b71e4374722a530d5bb14c74c5cc0a3","tid":524035,"uid":31841,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T07:29:23.000Z","msg":"咪傻啦<br />\n上去Marriott 個網睇睇先啦<br />\n全部酒店地址都係HK, China"},{"pid":"b83e09f26a27c185d93222e5b190a8ef3