店、萬怡酒店、喜來登酒店、威斯汀酒店和W酒店等30個品牌，據官網顯示，目前該集團在中國共有124家酒店。<br />\n<br />\n舉報發帖即時引起網民熱議，挑起網民的愛國心，有人提出要「共同抵制」、形容「看來是否想在中國開了」。不過亦有人提出「看你們能封殺多久」。<br />\n網民意見：<br />\n<br />\n朋友們都談戀愛去了：看來是不想在中國開了<br />\n<br />\n解憂雜貨店：記住這些名字，共同抵制<br />\n<br />\nAfter630：呀 腦子進水太多了吧！<br />\n<br />\n西野七l：分裂不能放過<br />\n<br />\n邰小銳銳：搞事情<br />\n<br />\n陳_腐乳_：又戳爆中國人的玻璃心<br />\n<br />\nliar_person：呵呵。。看你們能封殺多久<br />\n<br />\n蓉驕傲：送你上刑場 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25cfa377487ae170a7e457edbfd513c36b3e67e7","tid":524035,"uid":8040,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"83c28a58d8ddfad6e1518a7eae1be6e4fd52af58","tid":524035,"uid":36551,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7eed28048759b69921d36d71dbac73d0b471d91d","tid":524035,"uid":61462,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b83e09f26a27c185d93222e5b190a8ef32ca532c","tid":524035,"uid":77196,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T07:30:57.000Z","msg":"鄰國班五毛係咪好撚得閒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T08:21:17.000Z","msg":"啲on9支那人真係非常屎忽痕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T08:27:18.000Z","msg":"佢地搭飛機黎香港，見到要排國際線條隊，唔係國內線，會唔會又覺得係港獨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T09:16:16.000Z","msg":"佢地寫明係 國際線‧港澳台<br />\n<br />\n即刻自我感覺良好返"},{"pid":"9170420591d78d7e31691d7caf241cdb416eee21","tid":524035,"uid":13303,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T09:20:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 支那移動都係叫港澳台做國際"},{"pid":"908da2d5cc6945e17f5aa83d984d0d7476875b85","tid":524035,"uid":19126,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T09:30:29.000Z","msg":"鄰國根本係與世界為敵既低等人種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img